# Build context is the cloud-webapp/ root (api/Dockerfile builds from here), so
# this is the .dockerignore Docker actually applies. Keep the upload small and,
# critically, never ship incremental build caches: a *.tsbuildinfo without its
# matching dist/ makes `tsc -b` skip emit and fail with TS6305.
node_modules
**/node_modules
dist
**/dist
*.tsbuildinfo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
coverage
**/coverage
.git
.github
.vscode
.idea
*.log
.env*
**/test
**/.pytest_cache
**/__pycache__
**/.venv
